    "qualifications": "✅ Data-Driven Decision Making – 10+ years in data analysis, trend forecasting, and compliance reporting.\n✅ Blockchain & Crypto Expertise – Certified in Digital Assets Investigations, with experience in transaction monitoring.\n✅ Business Intelligence & Reporting – Skilled in SQL, Python, Power BI, and financial analytics.\n✅ Process Optimization & Transparency – Experience in automating workflows and ensuring",
